00:36:41,830 --> 00:36:47,180
♪Some shadows shimmer like stars♪

532
00:36:47,180 --> 00:36:51,970
♪Some memories linger in my heart♪

533
00:36:51,970 --> 00:36:57,090
♪Leaving me searching for hidden clues♪

534
00:36:57,090 --> 00:37:01,340
♪But there's no escape in the end♪

